OL,3,CNicola Sturgeon opens up about
OL,4,Csexuality and 'mental torture' of
OL,5,Carrest in book
OL,7,FNicola Sturgeon has opened up about
OL,8,Fhaving a miscarriage, her sexuality,
OL,9,Fand her arrest in a new book.
OL,11,FIn an excerpt of her memoir, Frankly,
OL,12,Fpublished by The Times, the former
OL,13,Ffirst minister of Scotland described
OL,14,Fbeing arrested and questioned by the
OL,15,Fpolice as "mental torture" and "the
OL,16,Fworst day" of her life.
OL,18,FMs Sturgeon was arrested in 2023 as
OL,19,Fpart of an investigation into the
OL,20,Ffunding and finances of the Scottish
OL,21,FNational Party.
