OL,8,Fchief executive of the SNP, was also
OL,9,Farrested and later charged with
OL,10,Fembezzlement, after his and Ms
OL,11,FSturgeon's home was searched by police
OL,12,Flooking into what happened to #660,000
OL,13,Fof donations to the party.
OL,15,FShe wrote of an "overwhelming" sense
OL,16,Fof relief and release upon being told
OL,17,Fshe would face no further action in
OL,18,FMarch 2025.
