OL,7,FThe former first minister also speaks
OL,8,Fcandidly about her miscarriage in
OL,9,F2010, saying she went to work in
OL,10,FJanuary while she was in "constant
OL,11,Fagony", including a memorial event for
OL,12,Fthe 40th anniversary of the Ibrox
OL,13,Fdisaster.
OL,15,FMs Sturgeon said she found out she was
OL,16,Fmiscarrying while receiving a flu jab
OL,17,Fon December 30 of that year, which led
OL,18,Fto an urgent appointment at Glasgow
OL,19,FRoyal Infirmary the following day.
