OL,7,F"I think I'd known in my heart what
OL,8,Fthe outcome would be, but I was still
OL,9,Fhoping for the best," she wrote.
OL,11,F"It seemed that suddenly, belatedly, I
OL,12,Fwanted to be pregnant after all. The
OL,13,Fnurse who did the scan was lovely."
OL,15,F"I didn't really know what I was
OL,16,Flooking for on the screen, but her
OL,17,Fface told me what I needed to know.
OL,18,FThe baby was gone."
